365
00:30:42,349 --> 00:30:44,551
As it always has been.

366
00:30:44,584 --> 00:30:46,286
Solid like iron.

367
00:30:47,888 --> 00:30:49,356
Unchanging.

368
00:30:50,524 --> 00:30:53,193
<i>You will fail.</i>

369
00:30:53,226 --> 00:30:56,930
