393
00:33:06,593 --> 00:33:08,161
<i>And open.</i>

394
00:33:09,596 --> 00:33:13,467
Oh! Is that mine?

395
00:33:13,500 --> 00:33:16,369
- As soon as you pass the test.
- I love it.

396
00:33:16,403 --> 00:33:20,474
